      "id": "PopularPost108561",
      "post_content": "I know that four mana for a 0/2 sounds awful, but trust me, this thing is amazing. I once drew half my deck in one turn, and that was without Skullclamps! My opponent had time to go get coffee and a bagel while I was busy drawing.",
      "posted_by": "Weary_PSI",
