    {
      "id": "PopularPost17040",
      "post_content": "This guy has a weak body, but it can provide great card advantage.  \n  \n[Bauble](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bauble)s (or low mana artifacts in general) are especially useful with that guy.  \nOr you imprint an artifact creature in [Semblance Anvil](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Semblance Anvil) and go crazy with artifacts that cost ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol) or less -  \nin this case you can also cast this guy on the subsequent turn for ![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol)![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol) if you haven't done this yet.  \nAnd then finish off with [Arcbound Ravanger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Arcbound Ravanger) for example.",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost17040\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">This guy has a weak body, but it can provide great card advantage.<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Bauble\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bauble\">Bauble</a>s (or low mana artifacts in general) are especially useful with that guy.<br/>Or you imprint an artifact creature in <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Semblance Anvil\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Semblance Anvil\">Semblance Anvil</a> and go crazy with artifacts that cost <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"2\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=2&amp;type=symbol\"/> or less -<br/>in this case you can also cast this guy on the subsequent turn for <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Blue\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=U&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Blue\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=U&amp;type=symbol\"/> if you haven't done this yet.<br/>And then finish off with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Arcbound Ravanger\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Arcbound Ravanger\">Arcbound Ravanger</a> for example.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '17040'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\"