    {
      "id": "PopularPost120311",
      "post_content": "cast [Mox Opal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mox Opal), draw one, tap for W, [glinthawk](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=glinthawk) for W returning Mox Opal, I draw again, cast Mox Opal again for zero, draw one and add U to my mana pool, use that U to activate [Master Transmuter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Master Transmuter) and wait I guess I don't draw a card for putting out my [Sphinx of the Steel Wind](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sphinx of the Steel Wind), oh well.  \nYah this guy can be nuts.",
      "posted_by": "TPmanW",
