    {
      "id": "PopularPost140013",
      "post_content": "[sensei's divining top](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=sensei's divining top), [lantern of insight](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lantern of insight), [etherium sculptor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=etherium sculptor), other cheap artifacts  \nadd [Jace's Erasure](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jace's Erasure) and your opponent will rarely draw anything useful.  \n  \n@lyoncet, sadly, lands won't trigger the ability since they aren't spells.",
      "posted_by": "roguepariah",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost140013\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\"><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"sensei's divining top\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=sensei's divining top\">sensei's divining top</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"lantern of insight\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lantern of insight\">lantern of insight</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"etherium sculptor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=etherium sculptor\">etherium sculptor</a>, other cheap artifacts<br/>add <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Jace's Erasure\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jace's Erasure\">Jace's Erasure</a> and your opponent will rarely draw anything useful.<br/><br/>@lyoncet,  sadly, lands won't trigger the ability since they aren't spells.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '140013'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy36774\">roguepariah</span>\r\n                                (2/26/2011 9:45:30 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating